import React from 'react';
import './Biography.css';

const Biography = () => {
    return (
        <section className="biography">
            <h2>Biography</h2>
            <p>
                Virat Kohli, born on 5 November 1988, is an Indian cricketer and the former captain of the Indian national team. Widely regarded as one of the best batsmen in the world, Kohli is known for his aggressive batting style and consistency. He made his debut for India in 2008 and has since broken numerous records in all formats of the game.
            </p>
            <p>
                Over the years, Kohli has been known for his remarkable performances in crucial matches. One of the most memorable knocks of his career came during the 2016 ICC T20 World Cup against Australia, where he scored an unbeaten 82 off 51 balls, leading India to a memorable victory. His ability to chase down targets has earned him the nickname "Chase Master."
            </p>
            <p>
                Kohli's contributions were instrumental in India's victory in the 2024 T20 World Cup. In the final against South Africa, he played a crucial innings, scoring 76 runs, which helped India secure the title. This win was a fitting testament to his illustrious T20I career, which he retired from after the tournament.
            </p>
            <p>
                Throughout his career, Kohli has amassed numerous records. He is the fastest player to score 8,000, 9,000, 10,000, 11,000, and 12,000 runs in ODI cricket. He has also scored the most centuries in successful run chases in ODIs and is the only player to average over 50 in all three formats of the game.
            </p>
            <p className="quote">
                "Self-belief and hard work will always earn you success." â€“ Virat Kohli
            </p>
            <p>
                Kohli's dedication to fitness and his aggressive yet focused demeanor on the field have made him an inspiration to many aspiring cricketers. His leadership has transformed the Indian cricket team into a formidable force in world cricket.
            </p>
        </section>
    );
};

export default Biography;
